    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <p>Thompson Carriage and Paint Shop was a nineteenth century Ypsilanti, Michigan business.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>The record group consists of account books and daybooks of the firm. Included is a record of log purchases, 1845-1853, and accounts of wheat purchased in 1842.</p>
    </scopecontent>
